descriptionNullable: The New York Times (nicknamed NYT and the Gray Lady) is an American daily newspaper based in New York City with a worldwide readership. The Times has won 132 Pulitzer Prizes, the most of any newspaper. It is ranked 18th in the world by circulation and 3rd in the U.S. This dataset brings information about all the 153.059 articles published between January 2020 and October 2022.
